---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How SmallGrid handles privacy and data." canonicalPath="/privacy/">
  <section class="card">
    <h1 style="margin:0 0 10px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="muted" style="margin:0 0 12px;">
      SmallGrid.uk is a simple informational site. We aim to collect as little personal data as possible.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin: 14px 0 8px;">What we collect</h2>
    <ul class="muted" style="margin:0; padding-left: 18px;">
      <li><strong>Server logs:</strong> like most websites, hosting providers may log IP address, browser type, and pages viewed for security and performance.</li>
      <li><strong>Emails you send us:</strong> if you email, we’ll receive your address and message content.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="margin: 14px 0 8px;">Advertising</h2>
    <p class="muted" style="margin:0;">
      This site may display advertising (e.g., Google AdSense). Advertising providers may use cookies or similar technologies
      to show relevant ads. See the Cookies page for details and consent information.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin: 14px 0 8px;">Analytics</h2>
    <p class="muted" style="margin:0;">
      If we add analytics in the future, we’ll aim for privacy-friendly options and update this policy.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin: 14px 0 8px;">Contact</h2>
    <p class="muted" style="margin:0;">
      Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@smallgrid.uk">hello@smallgrid.uk</a>.
    </p>

    <div class="hr"></div>
    <p class="muted" style="margin:0; font-size: 13px;">
      Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-GB", { year: "numeric", month: "long", day: "2-digit" })}
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
